Class Point3f

Object
Tuple3f
Point3f
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class Point3f extends Tuple3f
A three-dimensional point of float values.

We consider a point to be a tuple representing a single physical point in space.

Author:
Owen Feehan
